: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  committed financing</a> consists=C2=A0m=
ainly<em>=C2=A0</em>of (1) that $13 billion of debt=C2=A0from Morgan Stanle=
y et al., which they will have to fund, and (2) his own promise to put up=
=C2=A0$33.5 billion of his own money. But he=E2=80=99s allowed to syndicate=
