<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have not heard much about those equity comm=
itments in the last few months; when he was trying to get out of the deal f=
or alleged fraud, Musk did not have time to go around marketing it to poten=
tial co-investors. But now he could use the money. Like presumably he=E2=80=
=99s going to text Larry Ellison again to be like =E2=80=9Chey you=E2=80=99=
re still in for $1 billion right? Should be fun!=E2=80=9D What will those c=
onversations be like? Are those equity commitment letters still good?<a cla=
ss=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-6" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
