 creating X, the everything app.=E2=80=9D Choose wisely.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway I=E2=80=99m tired of this and I have a =
new retirement plan. Every time this newsletter starts with =E2=80=9CProgra=
mming note: Money Stuff will be off tomorrow,=E2=80=9D Musk does something =
outrageous, and Twitter=E2=80=99s stock swings up or down.=C2=A0So=C2=A0I=
=E2=80=99m going to buy a bunch of Twitter straddles and then take a vacati=
on, while Twitter is still public and that trick can still work.=C2=A0I=E2=
=80=99ll make a fortune.</p>
